translate ru TakeKhansHand_397e0921:
    # "Sarah reached out and placed her hand in his."
    ""

translate ru TakeKhansHand_a85e2571:
    # "Looking at it, it seemed like a joke to her, how small and frail her own body was compared to his."
    ""

translate ru TakeKhansHand_153682a9:
    # "And yet, he was gentle as he pulled her up to her feet."
    ""

translate ru TakeKhansHand_32c7b8e1:
    # "Sarah planted her hands on the bed and pushed herself up to her feet."
    ""

translate ru TakeKhansHand_2780bc7f:
    # "She made a point of him to notice her defiance, small as it was."
    ""

translate ru TakeKhansHand_179e9c76:
    # "Whatever it did to him, he gave no hint of it."
    ""

translate ru TakeKhansHand_389519b9:
    # "Following the Khan, Sarah weaved through the hallways of the sanctum until the room suddenly opened up before her."
    ""

translate ru TakeKhansHand_35270c76:
    # "The sight of the countless flowers and their infinite colours rushed across Sarah's senses, striking her mute."
    ""

translate ru TakeKhansHand_d991efc4:
    # "She had never seen anything like this in her life, and imagined she never would again if she ever left this place."
    ""

translate ru TakeKhansHand_39e80f16:
    # "As she followed Hassar deeper into the garden, she finally recovered enough to speak."
    ""

translate ru TakeKhansHand_84eaf180:
    # s "This is..."
    s ""

translate ru TakeKhansHand_1a2e09f8:
    # s "It's incredible."
    s ""

translate ru TakeKhansHand_448195c6:
    # "The Khan nodded as she slowly walked ahead of her."
    ""

translate ru TakeKhansHand_658e51f1:
    # "Sarah struggled to remind herself to maintain her humility, but found it equally impossible to cover her body."
    ""

translate ru TakeKhansHand_3fc7cc2a:
    # "In the end, she simply ceased trying."
    ""

translate ru TakeKhansHand_93c12634:
    # h "This garden took quite a while to construct."
    h ""

translate ru TakeKhansHand_bfcf08e9:
    # h "Many of the plants are native to my desert, but many more are from every corner of the world."
    h ""

translate ru TakeKhansHand_a9f49912:
    # h "The mechanics of the machinery that allows these various flowers to bloom is quite impressive."
    h ""

translate ru TakeKhansHand_ce3d53fa:
    # "He turned to face her."
    ""

translate ru TakeKhansHand_7101da98:
    # h "I can have my engineer bring you a book on the subject, should you find it interesting."
    h ""

translate ru TakeKhansHand_e319d300:
    # "Sarah nodded, though she knew little of engineering."
    ""

translate ru TakeKhansHand_c14f7eee:
    # "Finally, as they neared the center of the garden and were surrounded by flowers, the Khan sat down on a bench."
    ""

translate ru TakeKhansHand_812c6a93:
    # "He motioned for her to join him, and Sarah did. What choice did she really have."
    ""

translate ru TakeKhansHand_6ee42809:
    # "Sitting beside him so nakedly made her feel vulnerable, but she began to doubt that having clothes would change much to the situation."
    ""

translate ru TakeKhansHand_85a13d41:
    # "The man was a giant who towered even the strongest warriors. Next to her, he was like a mountain."
    ""

translate ru TakeKhansHand_70f9d140:
    # h "You asked me why I brought you here, and I shall be truthful with you, Sarah."
    h ""

translate ru TakeKhansHand_9068f59d:
    # h "I have ruled over the tribes for many years now, and I gathered many things."
    h ""

translate ru TakeKhansHand_8777534e:
    # h "Gold, jewels, horses. The wealth of empires has been laid before at my feet."
    h ""

translate ru TakeKhansHand_f07f35d4:
    # h "But you might be surprised to learn, I am not a man driven by avarice."
    h ""

translate ru TakeKhansHand_e9e31f81:
    # "Sarah looked at him as he spoke, hoping she might learn to understand the man that held the leash on her."
    ""

translate ru TakeKhansHand_b619a91f:
    # h "As I have risen, I have found that the world around me has begun to bend to my will."
    h ""

translate ru TakeKhansHand_dbba181a:
    # h "Advisors, generals, all nod along and say as I do, hoping to win my favors."
    h ""

translate ru TakeKhansHand_937ec3b6:
    # h "Increasingly, I feel alone. Isolated."
    h ""

translate ru TakeKhansHand_a7843aea:
    # "She watched as he looked across his garden."
    ""

translate ru TakeKhansHand_4c19bb86:
    # h "And so I sought to build a space in the world, small as it is, that I could truly call my own."
    h ""

translate ru TakeKhansHand_6102a6a7:
    # h "A place seperated from the world outside. A place that could remind me of who I am, where I can by myself without fear of showing weakness."
    h ""

translate ru TakeKhansHand_9ea16e3d:
    # "She watched as he lowered his head."
    ""

translate ru TakeKhansHand_e302267c:
    # h "My men imagine me near a god, but Sarah, I am as human as any other."
    h ""

translate ru TakeKhansHand_90ce09ee:
    # "Sarah observed him. How much of this was real. How much performance. Sarah wasn't sure of it."
    ""

translate ru TakeKhansHand_dee1f1d8:
    # s "So that's what I am then? A prized possession?"
    s ""

translate ru TakeKhansHand_a0a16463:
    # "He shook his head."
    ""

translate ru TakeKhansHand_26155f4d:
    # h "Quite the opposite. I want for you to be your own person. To exist in this space as freely as you would have outside of it."
    h ""

translate ru TakeKhansHand_5de915c2:
    # h "And in doing so, remind me of myself. Allow me to remember that I am still human, lest I fall over into blind arrogance."
    h ""

translate ru TakeKhansHand_34edc0e7:
    # "Sarah wanted to wilt under his dominating gaze, but she struggled to keep her eyes matching his."
    ""

translate ru TakeKhansHand_171b5dde:
    # s "The girls...they said you would not force yourself on me."
    s ""

translate ru TakeKhansHand_49d95595:
    # "Sarah felt him place one of his massive and powerful hands on her lower back as he looked down at her."
    ""

translate ru TakeKhansHand_c294f68d:
    # h "You are my guest, and I will treat you with all kindness that such a station demands."
    h ""

translate ru TakeKhansHand_c709a1e7:
    # h "You will not suffer a single injury. There is no force in this place."
    h ""

translate ru TakeKhansHand_65bec97b:
    # s "Does that mean that I am free to leave?"
    s ""

translate ru TakeKhansHand_a2de2fd5:
    # "The Khan shook his head."
    ""

translate ru TakeKhansHand_bce2c464:
    # h "No, not for now. Perhaps in time, when you have better settled in."
    h ""

translate ru TakeKhansHand_7c873a05:
    # h "The city is dangerous to those who do not know it. But should you want, I can show it to you in time."
    h ""

translate ru TakeKhansHand_6c3b9748:
    # "Sarah nodded. Perhaps she had pressed her luck too far with him."
    ""

